				<h3>INSTRUCTOR</h3>
				<img src="images/profile.jpg" id="images">
				<p class="catalog">
					Adrian Arnold grew up in North Philadelphia where violence was a constant element in the neighborhood.  He witnessed firsthand what happens to those who are unprepared to defend themselves and what they care about.  The consequences of being unprepared to defend oneself from violence can be deadly.  

					While searching for self-empowerment he began to study martial arts. Shortly thereafter the importance of applicability and and accessibility became apparent.  Overly complex movements will be confused and forgotten in a stress scenario.  Simplicity and proper training leads to higher ability to act.  Failure to act decisively brings about worst case scenarioos.  
				</p>
